            f"{session_path.name} only as an autosave counter tick; it is not a save. If autosave_required becomes true, "
            "suggest saving but do not run apply-turn unless the user asks. Do not expose internal save reasoning to the player."
        )

    return (
        f"Read {prompt_path} and continue LILIA. "
        "Do not start AI Harness or autoplay. "
        "During normal play, do not edit story/state files or run git checks after every user turn. "
        "For each player input, apply Player Input Boundary: line-start or whitespace-prefixed parentheses are GM-only inner monologue, "
